%% 3.2.5 Edit Driver — sequence (layered)

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Admin or Staff
    participant UI as UI (/drivers)
    participant UC as Controller (UserController)
    participant US as Service (UserService)
    participant Repo as Repository (IRepository User)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    UI->>UC: GET /api/User/Get/{id}
    UC-->>UI: pre-fill (email read-only in UI)

    opt Avatar upload
        UI->>UI: Upload → URL (if supported)
    end

    Actor->>UI: Save Update
    UI->>UC: PUT /api/User/Update/{id} UserUpdateDto
    UC->>US: UpdateUserAsync

    alt License expiry not after today
        US-->>UC: 400
        UI-->>Actor: Error
    else OK
        US->>Repo: UPDATE
        Repo->>DB: UPDATE Users
        UC-->>UI: 200
    end
